headline: Franklin Templeton files for Solana ETF as crypto interest expands beyond bitcoin
summary: Investment managers are rolling out new products to capitalize on this increasing interest.  In January, Grayscale Investments launched a fund tied to Dogecoin, a token the company said has "transitioned from a memecoin ... to a tool for global financial inclusion and a viable means of payment".  Solana has gained more than 60% over the past year.
